{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be playful and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Podcastify Network</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* AliceBlue, a light, playful blue-ish color */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* SteelBlue, our brand color */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: #b0c4de; /* LightSteelBlue, a softer blue */\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #333;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #4682b4; /* SteelBlue on hover */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #4682b4; /* SteelBlue */\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: #e6f0fa; /* Very light blue */\n            border: 1px solid #b0c4de; /* LightSteelBlue border */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(70, 130, 180, 0.3); /* SteelBlue shadow */\n        }\n        .podcast-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 150px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .podcast-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #4682b4; /* SteelBlue */\n        }\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* SteelBlue */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #5a9bd4; /* Lighter blue on hover */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* SteelBlue */\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Podcastify Network</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#podcasts\">Podcasts</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"about\">\n        <h2>Your Daily Dose of Fun & Insight!</h2>\n        <p>Welcome to Podcastify, where we bring you the most engaging, informative, and downright hilarious podcasts on the internet. From true crime mysteries to comedy chat shows, we've got something for everyone!</p>\n        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/87ceeb/ffffff?text=Podcastify+Banner\" alt=\"Podcastify Banner\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"podcasts\">\n        <h2>Our Top Shows</h2>\n        <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/add8e6/000000?text=Mystery+Makers\" alt=\"Mystery Makers\">\n                <h3>Mystery Makers</h3>\n                <p>Unraveling the world's most intriguing unsolved mysteries, one episode at a time.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/87ceeb/000000?text=Comedy+Corner\" alt=\"Comedy Corner\">\n                <h3>Comedy Corner</h3>\n                <p>Laugh out loud with our hilarious panel as they dissect pop culture and life's absurdities.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/6495ed/000000?text=Tech Trends\" alt=\"Tech Trends\">\n                <h3>Tech Trends</h3>\n                <p>Stay ahead of the curve with insights into the latest innovations and future of technology.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/4169e1/000000?text=Foodie Friends\" alt=\"Foodie Friends\">\n                <h3>Foodie Friends</h3>\n                <p>A culinary adventure exploring delicious recipes, restaurant reviews, and food history.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore All Podcasts</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Have a podcast suggestion or want to partner with us? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@podcastify.net\" style=\"color: #4682b4;\">info@podcastify.net</a></p>\n        <p>Follow us on social media!</p>\n        <p>\n            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #4682b4; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Facebook</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #4682b4; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Twitter</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #4682b4; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Instagram</a>\n        </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Podcastify Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}